{"tid":1993331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★綜援門檻由60歲提高至65歲，大批長者被迫重投職場！","createTime":"2020-04-28T16:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T10:59:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3d04d988c6f3d4d336d8524fe5f4c67294b540","tid":1993331,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"政府去年將綜援長者門檻由60歲提高至65歲，大批長者被迫重投職場！勞工及福利局今(28日)回應議員提問時透露，去年共有722名60歲以上的健全人士，經勞工處提供的轉介服務而獲聘，較前年激增62.6%。另外，勞工處的「中高齡就業計劃」去年成功協助417名60至64歲人士就業，較前年大增57.4%。<br />\n<br />\n勞福局指，去年有8101名健全求職人士，透過勞工處提供的轉介服務而獲聘，當中722人年齡為60歲以上，較前年大增逾60%。至於「中高齡就業計劃」，去年共有3061宗就業個案，涉及1093名僱主。截至去年12月，參加「中高齡就業計劃」成功就業的60歲以上個案中，最多人就業的是文書支援人員及清潔員，分別有71及37人；其次則為建造業，共有29人。至於最少人就業的是專業人員，僅4人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200428/bkn-20200428185755595-0428_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200428%2Fbkn-20200428185755595-0428_00822_001.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=66cfe60a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200428/bkn-20200428185755595-0428_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6678e8f1d534f03e0ba32c243bd6a17d63cd15e5","tid":1993331,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200428/photo/bkn-20200428185755595-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200428193846\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200428%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200428185755595-0428_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200428193846&h=102fe725&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0caf89c8dfb1a8f893578b3c7af13e8e8900f813","tid":1993331,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kJ7Ufw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kJ7Ufw.gif&h=ee5bd90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>